'From Squeak3.7alpha of 11 September 2003 [latest update: #5707] on 20 February 2004 at 4:28:42 pm'!"Change Set:		FixServerDirectories-nkDate:			12 December 2003Author:			Ned KonzChange Set 5605CleanupUpdateServers-dew did not clean up the ServerDirectory servers dictionary properly.This quickie will remove the bad servers."| badOnes |badOnes _ Dictionary new.ServerDirectory servers keysAndValuesDo: [ :k :v |	(v isKindOf: ServerDirectory) ifFalse: [ badOnes at: k put: v ] ].badOnes keysDo: [ :k | ServerDirectory servers removeKey: k ].!